{"word":"G5255 - ὑπήκοος - hypḗkoos - hoop-ay'-ko-os - Obedient","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπήκοος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypḗkoos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-ay'-ko-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Obedient</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கீழ்ப்படிந்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"giving ear, obedient"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5219 - ὑπακούω - hypakoúō - hoop-ak-oo'-o/5219\">G5219</a>; <i>attentively listening</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>submissive:</i> - obedient.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1522/1522\">G1522</a>, <a href=\"#/G1873/1873\">G1873</a>, <a href=\"#/G189/189\">G189</a>, <a href=\"#/G191/191\">G191</a>, <a href=\"#/G3876/3876\">G3876</a>, <a href=\"#/G3878/3878\">G3878</a>, <a href=\"#/G5218/5218\">G5218</a>, <a href=\"#/G5219/5219\">G5219</a>, <a href=\"#/G5255/5255\">G5255</a>"}]}